title: United Kingdom Imports of Man-made Staple Fibres
description: Imports of Man-made Staple Fibres in the United Kingdom increased to 37.84 GBP Million in September from 31.14 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Man-made Staple Fibres in the United Kingdom averaged 39.89 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 62.38 GBP Million in January of 2000 and a record low of 23.25 GBP Million in May of 2020. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Man-made Staple Fibres.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
